values
  ($q$01_FSC Manual Ver6_2$q$, NULL, '{"FY2025"}', $q$FSC COC Audit$q$, $q$01_FSC Manual Ver6_2.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jywHj-EcbQmx8AMJ_GJVqh3T_96PE4J6/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 1443626, $q$FSC COC Manual, Macromedia Digital Imaging Pvt. Ltd., Version 6.2, dated 27 June 2025. COC Administrator: Srinivas Babu Nandipa, AGM-Operations. OH&S Representative: Dr. GV Raju, Prasad CH. Covers: FSC COC training plan (6-month cycle) with list of trained employees by role/process; occupational health & safety ergonomic hazard assessment for prepress/printing/loading/post-production with MMDI's mitigations (2-person lift for rolls >25kg, roll jacks, hot-air seamers with long handles, XY digital cutter, digital routing machine); record-keeping system (5-year retention); FSC complaints mechanism (2-week acknowledgment, 3-month investigation); non-conforming product procedure (5-business-day notification to certification body); FSC product groups (P8.4 Advertising Materials, FSC Mix Credit / Transfer system); material sourcing verification via info.fsc.org; storage & segregation procedures; material balances / annual volume summary requirements; Transfer accounting system for determining FSC claims; conversion factor methodology (worked example: 100kg coated paper board -> 3073.83 SQFT, 25% total wastage); labelling/promotion approval via SCS; sales & delivery documentation requirements; outsourcing arrangement with Vijaya Paper Converters (jumbo reel to 100m roll conversion, agreement effective 12 Dec 2023); FSC-COC certified supplier list (Sappi Europe SA, cert SGSCH-COC-003171); Appendix 1 certificate details (Certificate Code SCS-COC-008291, License Code FSC-C164494, valid 2021-02-17 to 2026-02-17); Appendix 2 FSC-POL-01-004 self-declaration (signed 27 June 2025); timber legislation/trade/customs compliance section covering EUTR, EUDR/UDR (effective Dec 2025), Indian Customs Act 1962, DGFT/MoEFCC requirements, 5-year import record retention.$q$, now()),
  ($q$Timestamped_FSC-C015022$q$, NULL, '{"FY2025"}', $q$FSC COC Audit$q$, $q$Timestamped_FSC-C015022.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/17Z4V-rYGw6nS2Ihkz6A5ObMCpQa97eCI/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 338726, $q$FSC Certification Record for supplier Sappi Europe SA, License Code FSC-C015022, Certificate Code SGSCH-COC-003171 (old: SGS-COC-003171). Status: Valid. First issue Mar 29, 2007; last status update Jan 30, 2024; expiry Feb 15, 2027. Standards assessed: FSC-STD-40-003 V2-1, FSC-STD-40-004 V3-1. Due diligence system for FSC controlled wood: Yes. Lists ~16 group member sites (Sappi UK, Sappi Alfeld GmbH, Sappi Austria, Sappi Biochemtech, Sappi Ehingen, Sappi Finland, Sappi Italy Operations, Sappi Lanaken, Sappi Maastricht, Sappi Papier Holding GmbH, Sappi Pulp Americas, Sappi Rockwell Solutions, Sappi Stockstadt, Sappi Trading Australia) each with valid/expired status. Covers product categories from mechanical/chemical/dissolving pulp through copying/printing paper, newsprint, wrapping/packaging paper, specialty paper, tissue paper, coated paperboard, linerboard/testliner, fluting, roundwood, and twigs, each under FSC Controlled Wood / FSC Mix output categories with extensive tree species lists (Pinus, Eucalyptus, Populus, Betula, Fraxinus, Acer, Picea, Larix, Alnus, Fagus, etc.).$q$, now()),
  ($q$02_License_Agreement_Single_Certificate_Holder_English_only_V53_2017_(1)$q$, NULL, '{"FY2025"}', $q$FSC COC Audit$q$, $q$02_License_Agreement_Single_Certificate_Holder_English_only_V53_2017_(1).pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/18uOSWJffsBJFxfRSaL0TquIOkX_Wyc-G/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 2661179, $q$FSC License Agreement for the FSC Certification Scheme (v5.2, 12-2016) between FSC Global Development GmbH (Bonn, Germany) and Macromedia Digital Imaging Pvt Ltd (Plot No 23B & 24, Phase V, IDA Cherlapally, Hyderabad), represented by Managing Director Naresh Kumar Dasari. Grants MMDI a royalty-free, revocable, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use FSC Trademarks (checkmark-and-tree logo, 'FSC', 'Forest Stewardship Council') for on-product labeling and promotion, subject to CAB (Certification Body) approval. Covers definitions, license suspension/termination triggers (non-compliance within 12 months, reputational damage, policy violations), data processing/publication consent (FSC Database), Appendix 1 (Licensed Materials/trademarks), Appendix 2 (FSC-POL-01-004 self-declaration re: no illegal logging, no violation of human/traditional rights, no destruction of high conservation value forests, no forest conversion, no GMOs, no ILO Core Convention violations). Signed Hyderabad, 10-09-2020.$q$, now()),
