  ($q$11_MMDI FSC Material Input Summary from 10th July 2024- 25th June 2025$q$, NULL, '{"FY2025"}', $q$FSC COC Audit$q$, $q$11_MMDI FSC Material Input Summary from 10th July 2024- 25th June 2025.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KgQUnxH7uDMqG7QMF6Pw7OEQqMm4bLbn/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 447392, $q$MMDI Material Input Summary, period 10th July 2024 - 25th June 2025. Columns: Date, Invoice Number, Supplier Name & Address, Site, Material Name, Input Material FSC Claim, Certificate Code, Qty (KGs), Conversion Factor (SQFT). Sample entry: 02-12-2024, Invoice 124822407, Supplier Sappi Papier Holding GmbH (Brucker Strasse 21, A-8101 Gratkorn, Austria), Material Sappi Magno Satin 350 GSM Paper Board, FSC Mix Credit, Certificate SGSCH-COC-003171, Qty 5,598.00 KG, converted to 1,72,072.92 SQFT.$q$, now()),
  ($q$07_MMDI FSC COC Product Group list$q$, NULL, '{"FY2025"}', $q$FSC COC Audit$q$, $q$07_MMDI FSC COC Product Group list.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1lMGPJiWIYOLgAQlj6aYIn26Vc4Q8-blu/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 239427, $q$MMDI FSC COC Product Group List. Product Description: Catalogues, Flyers, Banners & Posters. Product code P8.4 (Printing, per FSC-STD-40-004a). Material category of input: 3.2 Coated Paper Boards. Primary activity: Printing. Material category of output: FSC Mix Credit / ONE Advertising Materials. Control system: Transfer.$q$, now()),
